    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the problem is i dont want to rest. resting just gives me more time to think about how much of a mess everything is. it's not even about being tired anymore, it's more like... the loop is just inevitable. no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. it feels like i'm just waiting for the crash.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
